description:
In the 3rd T20I, Sri Lanka and New Zealand went head-to-head at the Saxton Oval. New Zealand won the toss and asked Sri Lanka to bat first. Sri Lanka posted 218 runs on the board for 5 wickets in their 20 overs. A brilliant 101 runs knock from Kusal Parera helped the Lankans to achieve a huge score. The Kiwis got a decent start and faught tooth and nail to achieve the target but fell short by 7 runs. Rachin Ravindra was the star player from the Kiwis team scoring 69 valuable runs.

It stars Vishal, Anjali and Varalaxmi Sarathkumar in the leading roles, while Santhanam and Sonu Sood play other pivotal supporting roles. This paradox will blow your mind: Europeans are earning less than Americans тАУ an average EuropeanтАЩs income is nearly half that of an American ($44,368 vs. $81,695). Yet, Europeans rank higher on the Happiness Index, Life Expectancy, and Human Development Index.
HereтАЩs the kicker: even unemployed Europeans are almost as happy as employed Americans! Meanwhile, Americans, despite earning double, report lower happiness levels.
How is this possible? Is happiness truly linked to money, or are Europeans living proof that less can be more? Lets understand in depth, why EuropeтАЩs economy has fallen while it's happiness has soared. This is a mystery that could redefine what we currently value the most.

description:

Mannat Har khushi paane ki | Episode 1 | 06 January 25

Sonia abandons her newborn, but Shruti rescues the baby girl from the seashore and names her Mannat. Twenty-three years later, Mannat dreams of becoming the world's best chef. Will her journey lead her to uncover the truth about her past?

-------------------

Abandoned as a newborn by her own heartless mother and raised by her resilient maasi, Shruti, Mannat grows up to be a passionate and ambitious chef, unaware of her mysterious origins. Her journey intertwines with that of Vikrant, a successful buisnessman (restaurateur), as they bond over their love for cooking amidst the vibrant backdrop of Mumbai's chawls and elite culinary spaces. MannatтАЩs biological mother is none other than Aishwarya, a wealthy and manipulative woman determined to keep her secrets buried who is also Mannat's boss at Mezbaani where she works as a junior chef. Life takes a dramatic turn when Mannat discovers Shruti is not her biological mother, propelling her on a desperate quest to save ShrutiтАЩs life by finding her real mother for a liver transplant. Amidst these revelations, Mannat finds her strongest support in Vikrant, the prince charming of her life, who stands by her side, offering unwavering encouragement as she navigates the challenges life throws her way. As MannatтАЩs rising career, ShrutiтАЩs failing health, and the revelations of a hidden past collide, Mannat faces a whirlwind of love, betrayal, and self-discovery. Will her dreams and resilience help her overcome the storm, or will the weight of her past keep her from achieving her destiny?

Kaohsiung City Councilor Tang Yongyu\r

title: Bhogi Kundala muggulu ЁЯМ╕Simple Pongal Pot Koalm rangoliЁЯМ╕Sankranthi muggulu 2025 New designs Simple
description:
Bhogi Kundala muggulu ЁЯМ╕Simple Pongal Pot Koalm rangoliЁЯМ╕Sankranthi muggulu 2025 New designs Simple
It is our tradition to draw kolam every day morning at the doorsteps.
There are many benefits of drawing kolam in front of the house.
It is auspicious and believes Goddess Lakshmi enters the house if kolam is drawn.
Kolam brings a lot of positive vibrations and energy to you and your home.
Draw kolam soon after you wake up and then do your prayers.
Kolam or rangoli ( рд░рдВрдЧреЛрд▓реА  ) is a part of Indian culture and transferred from generation to the next generation.
This ancient art form is also called as muggulu in parts of South India like Andhra Pradesh and Telangana.
People draw different creative rangoli kolam designs using kolam powder or muggu pindi which is 
actually crushed Lime stone powder available in different parts of India.
There are different types of rangoli or kolam designs like dots kolam, sikku kolam, padi kolam, Margazhi kolam.
People draw special rangoli designs for Festivals like Sankranthi (Pongal), Diwali (Deepavali), Vijaya Dashami (Dasara).
Women create deepam rangoli or kolam designs during Diwali festival time, create very big and Dhanurmasam muggulu (Margazhi) for Sankranthi or Pongal festival.
It is a belief among the people that drawing muggulu in front of the house in the early morning soon after wake brings
good fortune to them and their family.
People mix rice flour to limestone powder and prepare their own kolam powder. Muggulu can also be drawn with rice flour only.
These Beautiful and creative designs are decorated with flowers based on the occasion or festival.

title: First Computer to QUANTUM COMPUTERS - Full Technology Evolution Explained
description:
Checkout LPU to learn new age skills - https://shorturl.at/VdcQ8 

Research references -  https://docs.google.com/document/d/1FS4NCssJYfQtDOlTsFr1FsLU6dV-D44JCmuwYWOl31k/edit?usp=drivesdk

The fastest supercomputer, El-Capitan, costing тВ╣5,000 crores, performs 2 quintillion calculations per second. However, itтАЩs about to be surpassed. GoogleтАЩs Quantum AI Chip "Willow" can process calculations 1 Nonillion (1 followed by 30 zeroes) times faster than todayтАЩs supercomputers. Tasks requiring 500 trillion times the universe's age for completion on current supercomputers can now be done in just 5 minutes. This breakthrough marks the beginning of a quantum computing revolution.
Quantum computing could unlock solutions to the universeтАЩs deepest mysteries, pinpoint alien life, enable light-speed travel, cure all diseases, extend human life to 150-200 years, and even achieve immortality by uploading consciousness into machines.
However, creating quantum computers as accessible as todayтАЩs systems remains a challenge. Companies like Microsoft, Amazon, IBM, and Intel are working to solve this, but GoogleтАЩs innovation puts it ahead in the race. This technology is poised to transform the impossible into reality.

title: EGG BONDA | MUTTAI BONDA | Road Side Evening Snacks Recipe Cooking In Village | Bajji Street Food
description:
In this video, we bring you the ultimate recipe for Egg Bonda (Muttai Bonda), a beloved roadside evening snack that everyone enjoys! Watch as we prepare this crispy, golden-brown delight in a traditional village setting, using fresh ingredients and time-honored cooking techniques.

The Egg Bonda is made by coating perfectly boiled eggs with a spiced gram flour batter and frying them to perfection. This mouthwatering snack is best enjoyed hot, with an evening. Whether you're a fan of street food or looking for a quick and tasty recipe to try at home, this video has you covered!

Get a glimpse of authentic village-style cooking and join us as we prepare this classic Indian snack in a scenic, peaceful atmosphere.

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, JethalalтАЩs Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

title: Mickey 17 | Official Trailer 2
description:
HeтАЩs dying to save mankind. #Mickey17 тАУ only in theaters March 7.

From the Academy Award-winning writer/director of тАЬParasite,тАЭ Bong Joon Ho, comes his next groundbreaking cinematic experience, тАЬMickey 17.тАЭ The unlikely hero, Mickey Barnes (Robert Pattinson) has found himself in the extraordinary circumstance of working for an employer who demands the ultimate commitment to the jobтАж to die, for a living.

Written and directed by Bong Joon Ho, тАЬMickey 17тАЭ stars Robert Pattinson (тАЬThe Batman,тАЭ тАЬTenetтАЭ), Naomi Ackie (тАЬStar Wars: Episode IX тАУ The Rise of SkywalkerтАЭ), Steven Yeun (тАЬNopeтАЭ), with Academy Award nominees Toni Collette (тАЬHereditaryтАЭ), and Mark Ruffalo (тАЬPoor ThingsтАЭ). 

The film is produced by Dede Gardner and Jeremy Kleiner (Oscar winners for тАЬMoonlightтАЭ and тАЬ12 Years a SlaveтАЭ), Bong Joon Ho and Dooho Choi (тАЬOkja,тАЭ тАЬSnowpiercerтАЭ). It is based on the novel Mickey 7 by Edward Ashton. The executive producers are Brad Pitt, Jesse Ehrman, Peter Dodd and Marianne Jenkins. The director of photography is Darius Khondji (Oscar nomination for тАЬBardo: False Chronicle of a Handful of Truths,тАЭ тАЬOkjaтАЭ). The production designer is Fiona Crombie (Oscar nomination for тАЬThe Favourite,тАЭ тАЬCruellaтАЭ). It is edited by Yang Jinmo (Oscar nomination for тАЬParasite,тАЭ тАЬOkjaтАЭ). The music is by Jung Jaeil (тАЬParasite,тАЭ тАЬSquid GameтАЭ). The visual effects supervisor is Dan Glass (тАЬFantastic Beasts: The Secrets of Dumbledore,тАЭ тАЬFast & Furious Presents: Hobbs & ShawтАЭ). The costume designer is Catherine George (тАЬOkja,тАЭ SnowpiercerтАЭ). 

Warner Bros. Pictures presents A Plan B Entertainment Production, An Offscreen Production / A Kate Street Picture Company Production, A Film By Bong Joon Ho: тАЬMickey 17.тАЭ The film will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures, in theaters only nationwide on March 7, 2025, and internationally beginning on 5 March 2025.

title: HIGHLIGHTS | PSG 4-2 MAN CITY | Grealish, Haaland Goals | UEFA Champions League
description:
City will need to beat Club Brugge next week to qualify for the Champions League play-off round after a 4-2 defeat to PSG.
The Blues saw a two -goal lead slip against the impressive French champions who responded with an outstanding fight-back

After a goalless first-half, quickfire second period goals from Jack Grealish and Erling Haaland looked to have set City on the road to a priceless victory.

But two goals in four minutes for PSG wiped out our advantage in the blink of an eye, a third from Joao Neves 12 minutes from time and a Gon├зalo Ramos fourth with the last kick of the game gave the Ligue 1 champions a dramatic 4-2 win.

Friends, hope you like today's vlog. See you soon with more interesting vlogs.

How to make canteen style toast sandwich recipe / toast sandwich recipe 

How to make Sandwich Chutney-
In a mixer grinder, add garlic, ginger, coriander, green chilies, mint leaves, lemon juice,bread pieces, chat masala, salt cold water , and churn it well. Don't make it too watery.┬а

Sandwich Stuffing-┬а
In a mixing bowl, add finely chopped onions, carrots, capsicum, add the chutney we made, 1 cup grated cheese, and mix well.┬а

For Sandwich-
Apply soft butter on bread, add the stuffing and spread it evenly. keep another slice of bread on top of it.┬а
Heat the grill pan, apply butter , keep the sandwich & cook until it turns crispy.┬а
